published on 2016-03-06T13:12:23Z

Kye Shand & Adam Taylor - Love on my mind 2. Example - All the wrong places - Steve Hill & Technikal Remix 3. Barely Legal - Such a Good Feeling (Elivate Remix) 4. Alf Graham & Dan Diamond - Kinda Funky 5. Shaun Williams - I Wanna Feel 6. Wizard - Inspiration 7. Phil Reynolds & the Coalition - Pumping 8. Parker & Clind - Generator - Ben Stevens Remix 9. JK & Technikal - Hideaway 10. Steve Hill & Technikal - Save the day 11. Flashnikal - L3T Go 12. Unit 13 - By The Way 13. Random but Raw & Sinobe - Abyss Sim0n53z Psy Slam Intro - Sim0n53z vs Binaural God of Death - Ex-Gen Warning - Khopat, Ex-Gen Closer - Ex-Gen Resistance is Futile - Jaws Underground Assistance Required - Absolum, Amush Invisible Invaders - Smashed Mutants - Ex-Gen, Absolum Lost - Jaws Underground Autopsy vs Ayanami - Loss of Consciousness
